snippet.title: BIND MORE  on (google play store)
snippet.description:
google play store :  https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=io.cordova.bindmore

BIND MORE 

-Simple challenging game.
-one or two players.
-its all about binding highest number of cells, you need to bind your cells as much close as possible and keep your challenger's cells detached.

download now and have fun :)
